#status <num> {text} [color]
  sets [colored] text of field <num> in status bar, numbered from 1
#status count <count>
  sets number of fields in status bar, from 0 to 10
#status size {<num>|all} {auto|fit|<len>}
  sets size of field <num> (or all fields at once)
    auto - size is set to 10 characters at startup and then extends to contents if needed
    fit - size is fitted to contents
    <len> - size is set to <len> characters
